					<description><![CDATA[Since 2018, the NSO has been engaged in the scrutiny of the all-party-parliamentary group (APPG) definition of ‘Islamophobia’. We gave evidence to the APPG on British Muslims and cited in their report Islamophobia Defined. Over the years we’ve been clear anti-Muslim discrimination must be tackled, like discrimination against any faith and those of no faith. &#8230;<br/><a href="https://nsouk.co.uk/nsos-decision-to-send-the-government-a-pre-action-protocol-letter-over-islamophobia/">Read more <span class="meta-nav">&#8594;</span></a>]]></description>
		
